paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the clinical characteristics and outcomes of cardiac amyloidosis in Saudi Arabia, focusing on transthyretin amyloid cardiomyopathy (ATTR-CA) and light chain amyloidosis (AL-CA). However, no specific genetic variants in the TTR gene are mentioned.

challenges: The paper did not provide specific genetic variant data for the TTR gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on clinical characteristics and outcomes without detailing specific TTR gene variants.
